==English==
===Etymology===
''[[classical]]'' + ''[[music]]''

===Noun phrase===
'''classical music'''
# {{music}} Music of the [[classical]] period; the music of [[w:Mozart|Mozart]], [[w:Haydn|Haydn]], etc; the musical period before the [[romantic]].
#(''informally'') the more [[serious]] forms of [[European]] and [[American]] music, as opposed to [[folk music]], [[jazz]] or the many forms of [[popular music]]

